title: How To Make Miracle Juice With The Breville Juice Fountain
description:
The Miracle Juice - Apple Beetroot and Carrot juice. 
It has gained massive popularity all over the world because of its magical health benefits.

Health Benefits:
- Boosts immune system
- Anti-Aging agents
- Can help in recovering from life threatening diseases
- Heart friendly
- Keeps cholesterol down
- Controls blood pressure
- Protects heart from many diseases
- Helps to clear up skin
- Helps regulate digestive system
- Sharpens memory
- Eliminates dryness/redness in eyes
- Aids in weight loss
